  "title": "Indulgent Middle Eastern Shredded Phyllo Knafeh",
  "description": "A classic Middle Eastern dessert-like dish made with shredded phyllo, cheese, and a tangy syrup. This version features a tagine-cooked syrup and a crunchy, sweet topping.",
